  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10445737472/hF6BBA2FF/dont-come-back-work-without-doctors-note\" id=\"_r_a_10445737472\" width=\"800\" height=\"420\" alt=\"\u0026#34;Don\u0026#39;t come back to work without a doctor\u0026#39;s note.\u0026#34;\" title=\"\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eOP didn’t automatically let her overstepping supervisor’s ridiculous attitude put her down and decided to question whether this demand was fair. In an attempt to be informed so she could stand her ground, she asked for Redditor\u0026#39;s advice.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e2\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10445725440/hDD8CC64D/ut-told-not-return-work-missing-optional-christmas-party\" id=\"_r_a_10445725440\" width=\"726\" height=\"129\" alt=\"[UT] Told not to return to work for missing optional christmas party.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e3\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10445725952/hC533C668/found-myself-an-unexpected-situation-at-work-after-missing-christmas-party-didnt-choose-attend\" id=\"_r_a_10445725952\" width=\"403\" height=\"247\" alt=\"I recently found myself in an unexpected situation at work. After missing a Christmas party I didn\u0026#39;t choose to attend, I was\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e4\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10445726208/hEA18A0BD/without-doctors-note-thing-is-actually-sick-but-whole-situation-still-feels-completely-unnecessary\" id=\"_r_a_10445726208\" width=\"417\" height=\"301\" alt=\"told not to return without a doctor\u0026#39;s note. The thing is, I actually was sick-but the whole situation still feels completely unnecessary.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e5\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10445726720/h5A89644D/hosting-christmas-party-today-which-presented-as-optional-opted-out-because-wasnt-planning-attend\" id=\"_r_a_10445726720\" width=\"412\" height=\"298\" alt=\"My workplace is hosting a Christmas party today, which was presented as optional. I opted out because I wasn\u0026#39;t planning to attend. I was\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e6\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10445727488/hB599DB7B/today-my-team-lead-asked-why-didnt-attend-explained-didnt-sign-up-go-and-wasnt-feeling-well-anyway\" id=\"_r_a_10445727488\" width=\"406\" height=\"307\" alt=\"blindsided today when my team lead asked why I didn\u0026#39;t attend. I explained that I didn\u0026#39;t sign up to go and wasn\u0026#39;t feeling well anyway.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e7\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10445727232/h45A9389B/dont-come-back-work-without-doctors-note-while-genuinely-unwell-demand-note-felt-excessive-do\" id=\"_r_a_10445727232\" width=\"405\" height=\"295\" alt=\"Their response? \u0026#34;Don\u0026#39;t come back to work without a doctor\u0026#39;s note.\u0026#34; While I was genuinely unwell, the demand for a note felt excessive. Do I\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e8\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10445726976/hA4E05A72/not-have-chance-speak-with-hr-first-shes-just-my-team-lead-she-has-boss-who-has-boss\" id=\"_r_a_10445726976\" width=\"408\" height=\"235\" alt=\"not have a chance to speak with HR first? She\u0026#39;s just my team lead, she has a boss who has a boss.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e9\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10445726464/hCBC5F382/scheduled-shift-or-critical-meeting-about-skipping-voluntary-social-event-didnt-realize-my-absence\" id=\"_r_a_10445726464\" width=\"415\" height=\"295\" alt=\"This wasn\u0026#39;t about missing a scheduled shift or a critical meeting-it was about skipping a voluntary social event. I didn\u0026#39;t realize my absence\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e10\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10445727744/hAAE8ECD8/would-require-medical-documentation-especially-since-had-never-committed-being-there-first-place\" id=\"_r_a_10445727744\" width=\"426\" height=\"241\" alt=\"would require medical documentation, especially since I had never committed to being there in the first place.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eAs you see, OP was wondering if she could go to HR or someone higher up about it, rather than just follow her team lead’s exceeding order. And like it usually does, the comment section did not disappoint, providing OP with a mash-up of solid advice and some \u003ca href=\"https://cheezburger.com/38279941/yall-are-my-heroes-for-real-international-swarm-of-callers-floods-scam-center-after-woman-shares-the\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003eabsolutely hilarious comebacks\u003c/a\u003e. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e11\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10445728000/h650D9D94/rredhead926-1d-ago-wri-top-1-comme-dont-need-doctors-note-show-up-work-as-normal-dear-hr-person\" id=\"_r_a_10445728000\" width=\"415\" height=\"363\" alt=\"Rredhead926 ⚫1d ago I wri... Top 1% Comme... You don\u0026#39;t need a doctor\u0026#39;s note. Show up to work as normal. **** Dear HR Person,\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003ea very unconventional case of \u0026#34;HR a day keeps the doctor away\u0026#34;\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cdiv\u003e\n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e12\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch2\u003eTo whom it may concern\u003c/h2\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10445728256/h2AB3E5F2/voluntary-gathering-did-not-attend-and-as-happened-felt-bit-under-weather-team-lead-seems-be-under\" id=\"_r_a_10445728256\" width=\"358\" height=\"280\" alt=\"My understanding is that the holiday party on DATE was a voluntary gathering. I did not attend, and, as it happened, I felt a bit under the weather. Team Lead seems to be under the\" title=\"To whom it may concern\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e13\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10445728512/h5684EEBD/doctors-note-just-wanted-check-and-see-if-our-wires-were-crossed-please-advise-thank-diamondvwn\" id=\"_r_a_10445728512\" width=\"370\" height=\"465\" alt=\"impression that the party was a mandatory work event and informed me that I should not return to work unless I provided a doctor\u0026#39;s note. I just wanted to check in and see if our wires were crossed. Please advise. Thank you, Diamondvwn\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e14\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10445728768/h81751AD5/13h-ago-oh-bring-back-doctors-note-alright-one-assigning-unlimited-stress-leave-at-their-demands\" id=\"_r_a_10445728768\" width=\"415\" height=\"319\" alt=\"Safe Word 9999 • 13h ago Oh I\u0026#39;d bring back a doctors note alright One assigning me unlimited stress leave at their demands\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e15\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10445729280/h2A1BB009/work-culture-people-are-less-inclined-want-be-part-theyre-destroying-work-culture-by-s-t-like-this\" id=\"_r_a_10445729280\" width=\"430\" height=\"397\" alt=\"• Callan_LXIX 8h ago • managers need to recognize that forcing situations and then penalizing as well; make for a work culture that people are less inclined to want to be a part of. They\u0026#39;re destroying work culture by s--t like this.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5B